as well as the little gifts you mentioned like cups and scarves,

35
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:27,000
I think even if there is something between the two of them, it probably just started.

36
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:30,800
It can't start though! There can't be anything at all!

37
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:35,700
As a person who has some experience in these kinds of things, I'm advising her to calm down.

38
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:38,300
First, you have to  think about what you will do in the future

39
