163
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:14,120
Are you guys doing well?

164
00:17:14,120 --> 00:17:16,460
I'm great, Mom.

165
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:18,790
Are you well?

166
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:22,820
I'm great. After getting home, the water and air have been great,

167
00:17:22,820 --> 00:17:26,210
 so my health is much better now. All right, 

168
00:17:26,210 --> 00:17:29,980
I will hang up now. I have to go and dance.

169
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:57,290
Brother Yang, are you here?

170
00:17:57,290 --> 00:17:59,590
Earlier, your wife called and scolded me.

171
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:02,050
It's fine. For you, I don't care.

172
00:18:02,050 --> 00:18:05,040
Even if the whole world scolds me, I won't be afraid.

173
00:18:05,040 --> 00:18:07,670
