177
00:18:15,990 --> 00:18:19,670
Brother Yang, even if we cannot be together in this lifetime,

178
00:18:19,670 --> 00:18:22,770
I will never forget the love you've given me

179
00:18:22,770 --> 00:18:25,710
 during this time.

180
