225
00:25:50,540 --> 00:25:52,580
Mom!

226
00:25:53,500 --> 00:25:55,210
Coming.

227
00:26:01,270 --> 00:26:03,050
What are you doing?

228
00:26:03,050 --> 00:26:07,010
Why are you pulling on me? This is a new jacket. It's very expensive!

229
00:26:07,670 --> 00:26:09,520
