230
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:11,380
Can't you let her make her own decision?

231
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:15,530
Li Siyu, can you not always think about things from your own perspective?

232
00:26:15,530 --> 00:26:17,670
Zhizhi is not you or me.

233
00:26:17,670 --> 00:26:20,220
This family is her life. She cannot survive without this family.

234
00:26:20,220 --> 00:26:24,350
Zhizhi was very independent when she was young. She became like this after being with Liu Yang.

235
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:27,630
- Can you get her to go back to when she was young? 
 - She cannot rely on that man.

236
00:26:27,630 --> 00:26:29,660
Maybe it's good for her to leave him.

237
00:26:29,660 --> 00:26:31,780
- How about the kid? 
 - I can help her take care of the child.

238
00:26:31,780 --> 00:26:34,800
Don't indulge in the wildest fantasy. Are you someone who can lead a family life?

239
00:26:34,800 --> 00:26:37,870
Do you want Yuwei to eat takeout food with you?

240
00:27:14,530 --> 00:27:16,300
Zhizhi,

241
