I don't know.

243
00:27:24,710 --> 00:27:28,740
If you don't want to, then ask him to come back.

244
00:27:28,740 --> 00:27:32,100
Siyu slapped him. Consider it as venting your anger.

245
00:27:32,100 --> 00:27:34,880
I think he won't dare to hit you again.

246
00:27:40,090 --> 00:27:41,790
Yiming said that

247
