359
00:38:02,300 --> 00:38:05,200
I tried to persuade her to rest

360
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:09,400
but she thinks I'm forcing her to resign.

361
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:12,200
That's not what I mean, but

362
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:14,800
she just keeps trying to go against me.

363
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:16,900
Resigning is a huge thing.

364
00:38:16,900 --> 00:38:21,600
Yes, but I wasn't trying to make her resign.

365
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:25,000
I just think that she needs to first better her health.

366
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:28,200
Once she is better, she can start working again,

367
00:38:28,200 --> 00:38:31,900
